comes, read-only status display in edit mode, API error display, `exactOptionalPropertyTypes`-safe payload construction\n- **`RcdoBreadcrumb.tsx`** — Accessible `<nav aria-label=\"RCDO path\">` breadcrumb with clickable ancestor nodes and `aria-current=\"page\"` on the selected node\n- **`ArchiveConfirmDialog.tsx`** — Modal dialog with impact explanation; disabled confirm button and explicit blocked message when node has active children\n- **`MoveNodeDialog.tsx`** — Re-parent dialog showing only valid non-archived parents of the correct type; blocks Rally Cries from being moved\n\n### Updated page\n- **`src/routes/Rcdos.tsx`** — Full two-panel layout: left (search + status filter radio group + tree), right (empty state / node detail + actions / create form / edit form). Permission hooks derive Admin/Manager/IC from `featureFlags.rcdoAdminEnabled` and `featureFlags.managerReviewEnabled`. Archive dialog opens with active-children detection. Move dialog available for non-Rally Cry nodes.\n\n### Tests (100 total)\n- **`__tests__/RcdoTreeView.test.tsx`** (24 tests) — hierarchy rendering, expand/collapse, expand-all/collapse-all, status filtering, search filtering, aria attributes\n- **`__tests__/RcdoNodeForm.test.tsx`** (22 tests) — required-field validation, parent selector per node type, target metric Outcome-only, edit mode pre-fill, API error handling\n- **`__tests__/RcdoPage.test.tsx`** (26 new tests) — loading/error states, selection, breadcrumb updates, archive dialog + active-children blocking, permission-based action hiding (IC/Manager/Admin)\n\n```observations\n- [low] frontend/src/components/rcdo/RcdoNodeForm.tsx: The \"Owner Team\" and \"Owner User\" fields accept free-text UUIDs. In a future step these should become proper selectors backed by a team/user API. For now they're text inputs with placeholder guidance.\n- [low] frontend/src/routes/Rcdos.tsx: The `rcdoAdminEnabled` feature flag is not declared in the `FeatureFlags` interface in shared/src/host.ts. 